18
00:01:25.770 --> 00:01:28.340
In this module,

19
00:01:28.340 --> 00:01:33.980
you learned about the basic API features to get started with creating

20
00:01:33.980 --> 00:01:38.700
and adding content to a PDF document in PDFBox.

21
00:01:38.700 --> 00:01:43.250
In addition, you learned about the PDF coordinate system,

22
00:01:43.250 --> 00:01:48.300
which is important when it comes to adding content in the PDF document.

23
